Uses of Package
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro

  • Packages that use edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro 
    Package Description
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB Macro Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.user
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB User Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.macro
    Contains Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB Macro Layer entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.user
    Contains Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB User Layer entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.user.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.macro
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB macro repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.macro.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.user
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB user repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.user.
  • Classes in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro used by edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro 
    Class and Description
    Content
    Content entities represent the content of Contribution and Context entities.
    Contribution
    A Contribution entity is a representation of a contribution in a discussion space such as a forum post, chat message or equivalent discourse artifact.
    ContributionAudience 
    ContributionContext
    This relation entity associates a contribution c with another contribution or content that represents the context of c.
    Discourse
    A Discourse represents the broad context of interactions that might come from multiple datasets.

    A DiscoursePart represents a distinct sub-space within a Discourse.
